<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="official-adj">official <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'fɪʃl/    美 /ə'fɪʃl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[只用于名词前] 公职的；公务的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>official responsibilities 
公务</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The foreign minister will make <strong>an official visit</strong> to Tokyo. 
外交部长将前往东京进行正式访问。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常用于名词前] 官方的；正式的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an official announcement
官方公告</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an official day's holiday
法定节假日</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>English is one of the official languages used in India.
英语是印度使用的官方语言之一。</p><footer>人教① – 2</footer></div></div>